import React from 'react' // import Link from 'next/link' type propsType = { name: string, tags: string[], number_of_reviews: number, rating: number, } const Attraction = (props: propsType) =>

{props.name}

{props.tags.join(', ')}

{props.number_of_reviews} - {props.rating}

export default Attraction
